<LegalLayout
  title="Cookie Policy"
  description="Cookie policy for By Shakir Luxury Interiors. Information about how we use cookies on our website."
>
  <h2>1. What are cookies?</h2>
  <p>
    Cookies are small text files placed on your computer or mobile device by websites. They help
    sites function properly and provide information to site owners.
  </p>

  <h2>2. Does this website use cookies?</h2>
  <p>
    No tracking or advertising cookies are used. We rely on privacy-friendly technology and
    deliberately avoid cookies for analytics or ads.
  </p>

  <h2>3. Website analytics</h2>
  <p>
    To understand how visitors use our website, we use <strong>Cloudflare Web Analytics</strong>.
    This service is designed with privacy in mind:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>No cookies are placed</li>
    <li>No personal information is collected</li>
    <li>IP addresses are not stored</li>
    <li>Visitors are not tracked across websites</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    More information: 
    <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/web-analytics/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      cloudflare.com/web-analytics
    </a>.
  </p>

  <h2>4. Essential technical storage</h2>
  <p>
    Some technical data may be stored temporarily in your browser for the site to work properly, such
    as:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Local storage for mobile menu state</li>
    <li>Session data for form handling</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    This data is not used for tracking and is cleared automatically by your browser.
  </p>

  <h2>5. Third-party services</h2>
  <p>
    Our website uses a few external services with their own privacy and cookie policies:
  </p>

  <h3>Google Fonts</h3>
  <p>
    We load fonts from Google Fonts. Google receives limited technical data (such as IP address and
    browser details) to deliver the fonts. More information:
    <a href="https://developers.google.com/fonts/faq/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      Google Fonts Privacy
    </a>.
  </p>

  <h3>Web3Forms</h3>
  <p>
    Our contact form is processed by Web3Forms. Their privacy policy is available at
    <a href="https://web3forms.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      web3forms.com/privacy
    </a>.
  </p>

  <h2>6. Your choices</h2>
  <p>
    Because we do not use tracking cookies, a cookie banner is not required. You remain in control of
    your privacy while browsing our site.
  </p>

  <h2>7. Changes</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this cookie policy from time to time. Changes will be published on this page.
  </p>

